The paper discusses the concept of Software Defined Networks (SDNs) and its impact on computer networks. This topic falls under the category of computer networks and internet architecture, which is covered by cs.NI. The paper also touches upon security concerns (cs.CR), data center networks (cs.DC), system and control theory (cs.SY), and information theory (cs.IT).
